A merit good? e.g.
 subsidized condoms.
 
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

 are high risk types.
 But they like risk so 
\begin_inset Formula $h<l$
\end_inset

.
 Could also be richer so 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{H}>y_{L}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

