\begin_inset Formula $C_{s}=\sum_{t}c_{I\left(s,t\right),t}$
\end_inset

 denotes the number of years under a connected governor, 
\begin_inset Formula $i=I\left(s,t\right)$
\end_inset

 returns the identity of the governor 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

