Share of connected governors with at least 6 years of tenure when a colony
 becomes vacant is an instrument:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{t}=\frac{\sum_{i}\mathbf{1}\left\{ T_{it}\geq6\right\} \times c_{it}}{\sum_{i}\mathbf{1}\left\{ T_{it}\geq6\right\} }
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Expected number of connected appointments is then 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{s}=\sum_{t}p_{t-1}\times\mathbf{1}\left\{ T_{I\left(s,t\right),t}=1\right\} $
\end_inset


